dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for Langlade County, Wisconsin in 2021. [Address points represent invididual address locations with permanent improvements some of which have been field verified. Purpose: The address points are used in geocoding valid locations within Langlade County. These are essential for critical functions such as emergency response and dispatch. Maintenance and Update Frequency: Quarterly depending on demand for new or modified addresses. Last Update: Dec, 2020]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
